<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Die heilige Johanna der Schlachthöfe</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Die Gewehre der Frau Carrar</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Mutter Courage und ihre Kinder</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Die Tage der Kommune)</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Der Dreigroschenroman</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
'>Kalendergeschichten</span></p>
<p style='line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;
